data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Sellers are offering $5,000 in Buyers concessions.    This immaculate 4 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage home is situated on a corner lot with a pool and spa, making it perfect for entertaining.  The stunning open kitchen features a breakfast nook, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and vaulted ceilings. Both bathrooms have been recently updated with new vanity sinks, and modern touch button LED anti-fog vanity wall mirrors. The master bathroom also has a walk-in shower.  Master bedroom has access to lanai/pool/spa, and recently updated walk in closet. The spacious living room opens to the lanai/pool/spa with French doors. There is brand new carpet in all bedrooms, new hot water heater, and the roof was replaced in 2019. The swimming pool is salt water with a new pool pump, and new salt cell for trouble-free operation.  This property is located close to schools, shopping, restaurants, and the YMCA. The community also offers a variety of amenities including tennis courts, racquetball, basketball courts, parks, and a playground.  Plus, no CDD and very low HOA. Don't miss out on this opportunity and schedule your showing today!
